arts.ttl: Euro 2025: Unbeaten Spain overcomes Italy which also advances to quarterfinals
arts.sum: Spain leveled within four minutes, led from the 49th, and added Esther González’s tournament-leading fourth goal in stoppage time. She leveled in the 14th, finishing a move she started with a right-foot shot curled into the top corner.
